    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This BMW E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the S54B32 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual and a variable M differential lock. Mechanical stewardship is evident: rod bearings have been addressed with treated shells, the rear subframe is reinforced with plates, and the VANOS unit has been overhauled. It retains excellent compression across all cylinders and a sharp, linear throttle response. While the exterior shows the honest patina of a well-loved driver, the chassis dynamics and powertrain synchronization remain tight and communicative. An exceptional entry point for the serious enthusiast looking for a mechanically sound apex-carver.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
