    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a prime example of a reliable, high-quality daily driver. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish with only minor, age-appropriate road chips that do not detract from its sharp curb appeal. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the premium upholstery shows minimal wear, and all cabin electronics\u2014including the infotainment system, dual-zone climate control, and heated seats\u2014function exactly as they should. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, having recently passed a comprehensive multi-point inspection and a full synthetic oil service. The tires provide ample grip with approximately 75% tread life remaining, and the brake pads were replaced within the last year. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that comes with a complete folder of service receipts and two sets of keys. It is ready for the road and requires no immediate investment.",
      "price": 34800.0,
